+// a typo or a missing file, so the compiler warns (and leaves layouts
+// unchanged) instead of silently doing nothing.
+//
+// RUN: %clang_cc1 -std=c++20 -fcxxmg -fcxxmg-field-profile-use=%t.no-such-file -fsyntax-only %s 2>&1 | FileCheck %s
